name: Duskfall Project Virtual
description:
If you want to donate towards costs and don't want to subscribe:

https://ko-fi.com/DUSKFALLcrew

If you want to monthly support the EARTH & DUSK media projects and not just AI:

https://www.patreon.com/earthndusk

Discord: https://discord.gg/Da7s8d3KJ7

A cross between:
1. Redshift Diffusion
2. Project Unreal Engine
3. Duskfall Virtual 3D Diffusion

If you like what we've got for our merged and other models consider donating: https://patreon.com/earthndusk

  • DO NOT SELL THIS MODEL, OR MERGES

  • Do merge, and do enjoy.

  • Generative images for commercial use are fine.

  • Credit in your merges would be great.

The configuration file included is probably required? XD
If it's ANY different than the one we were provided with Project Unreal, then cool - it automatically renamed them on merging.

modelVersions.description: While there is a "PART TWO" they are slightly different in how they were merged. This one does NOT have the extra Duskfall Portal Crew or Duskfall AI models merged in.
